Kazatomprom’s ULBA Plans to Raise Beryllium Price, Interfax Says

-- B y   N a r i m a n   G i z i t d i n o v
-- 
2011-03-01T12:31:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-01/kazatomprom-s-ulba-plans-to-raise-beryllium-price-interfax-says.html
ULBA Metallurgical Plant, a uranium-
pellet producing unit of  Kazakhstan ’s state-owned Kazatomprom,
will increase beryllium products prices by 5 percent to 8
percent on June 30, Interfax reported, citing an unidentified
company official.  To contact the reporter on this story:
